sentence.text: We conducted a interleukin-7-mediated signaling pathway-expression quantitative trait loci (cis-eQTL) analysis using normal or tumor breast transcriptome data from the Molecular Taxonomy of Breast Cancer International Consortium (METABRIC), The Cancer Genome Atlas (TCGA), and the Genotype-Tissue Expression (GTEx) project.

Furthermore, we performed inÂ vitro assays in breast cancer cell lines, and our results indicated that telomere maintenance, apoptotic process, and protein modification by small protein conjugation played a vital role in breast tumorigenesis via certain disruption of cell behaviors.
